373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"西貢結界"},{"pid":"a08db27cf989de59484ca4cb3a5d362c805b674c","tid":464883,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed89e337113cfe61b20e73c182b23c413a7cce17","tid":464883,"uid":35368,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"以為有藍田果條龍"},{"pid":"a4d995fe7a02321139f771d062918c16836d3cb1","tid":464883,"uid":53026,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"六：曾蔭權篤信風水，仍官司纏身"},{"pid":"e20e90aa835bb99299b49e03ecee462183960f5f","tid":464883,"uid":49197,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我開台播過次夜夜痴纏, 有個巴打係我個台聽到話出事, <br />\n之後要播返隻秦始皇先震得住</blockquote><br />\n大地在我腳下! 國計掌於手中! 哪個再敢多~說~話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !?"},{"pid":"931c02753d8f7e8fdc5ea26c92d127e45eccbaac","tid":464883,"uid":59700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"早排881余宜發都有播夜夜痴纏啦"},{"pid":"3a5f9a2d61d50ae43d07f8d416e5e3d22dfad5d4","tid":464883,"uid":49197,"like":6,"dislike":27,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"根說石龜因吸收了日月精華，已經修練成精。石龜由海濱的方一直向山頂爬行，每年會向上爬行一寸，當它爬行到太平山頂時，處於九龍及香港的整條龍脈就會醒覺，令到整個香港及所有島嶼陸沉。後來亦指原來石龜爬得愈高，香港經濟會愈差，所以1997年中、英政權交接時，中方就派出<span style=\"color: red;\">一位大師破此格局</span>。後來香港會議展覽中心新翼公布建築模型後，市民紛紛認為石龜下海，亦說香港太空館是它的龜蛋；電影《行運超人》內亦有記述這傳說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果當年大軍唔係為咗破呢個局損耗咗大半功力,就唔會輸比周星祖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98224b7218e766916139db97935c9c5502a0f205","tid":464883,"uid":37528,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"香港最恐怖既野係：共產黨"},{"pid":"0230ad9529b9cc133eb6590419f9754b70fd422e","tid":464883,"uid":37528,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我開台播過次夜夜痴纏, 有個巴打係我個台聽到話出事, <br />\n之後要播返隻秦始皇先震得住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知唔知醜呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31f0bd9d754e7eee79df7dce84ac19cf02bdefa","tid":464883,"uid":102096,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c80dc4a1af64e72d3926ff25ea8b4bb2e7ae2e34","tid":464883,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都市傳說五：電台禁播《夜夜痴纏》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1984年上映，由周潤發、葉蒨文、黃百鳴主演的電影《靈氣迫人》，當時被稱為票房毒藥的周潤發，竟然突然電影成為千萬票房明星，而主題曲《夜夜痴纏》亦成了不少fans最喜愛的歌曲。不過，最終《夜夜痴纏》亦成了電台禁歌之一，原因是不少DJ在夜深時分播放這歌都會發生奇怪事件，而當中有位港台的DJ分享，在播放時聽到一把女人慘叫聲，後來聽眾要求重播時一樣聽到鬼聲，後來其他DJ由此都將這歌列為禁歌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HL4u4aKYkbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHL4u4aKYkbY&d=7VTm%2BqeeYZz6%2BOv%2BOZ%2BwxJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5a7da5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HL4u4aKYkbY</a></blockquote><br />\n小巴佬都唔播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔敢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efb28ad64211cfa8875c65837b976fed7428432","tid":464883,"uid":37528,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大頭怪嬰呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年好震撼<br />\n仲有無主孤魂個牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e9d10f07ce8e7d54f5ead0a9cb15b12ab5dc68","tid":464883,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"首歌以前雷雨揚個鬼故節目拎黎做主題曲"},{"pid":"54772842bed6161b4a58a0fd9cd412f13fe56c8c","tid":464883,"uid":43173,"like":2